    <div id="mainContent">
        <h1>Mekton Zeta Designs</h1>
        	
<p>Welcome to my Mekton design page. The mecha designs presented here are in a text form based on the play sheet from <cite><a href="http://www.best.com/%7Ertg1/mekton.html">Mekton Zeta</a></cite>. Most of these designs are from <cite><a href="http://www.anime.net/macross/">Macross</a></cite>, but some designs from <cite><a href="http://www.gundamofficial.com/">Gundam</a></cite> are being added. <cite>Macross</cite> designs are grouped according to their first significant appearance.</p>

